{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_04_02",
  "title": "白石千紗",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千紗がデザイナーと打ち合わせをした、翌日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それでデザイナーさんとの打ち合わせは\nどうだったんだ？",
      "startTime": 5.865253739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私の考えたデザインは全部不採用でした……",
      "startTime": 7.2889299233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "「これは白石姉妹の衣装じゃない」って\nデザイナーさんに言われて……",
      "startTime": 16.0590567529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして{user}さんは\nこうなることが分かってたんですか？",
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "予想はしていたよ\n千紗はどうして不採用になったか分かるか？",
      "startTime": 25.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……ユニットの衣装なのに\nお姉ちゃんに合うデザインばかり考えていて……",
      "startTime": 33.0210198406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私に似合うかどうかは考えてなかったから……",
      "startTime": 36.9889299233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。デザイナーさんも\nそこに気付いてほしかったんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 44.0234867016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今度のユニットは\n私よりお姉ちゃんが前に出た方がいいと思うんです！",
      "startTime": 49.1664207345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "子供の頃、私の前で歌ってくれた時みたいに\nお姉ちゃんには眩しいくらい輝いてほしいんです",
      "startTime": 57.0391519024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、お姉ちゃんをもっと立てて\n衣装もお姉ちゃんに合わせた方が……",
      "startTime": 63.6305536341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "このユニットは千紗と沙季の二人が主役だ\nどちらか片方だけを優先するのがいいとは思えないな",
      "startTime": 70.3168789204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "それは……。そうですね……分かりました……\n新しいデザインを考えてみます……",
      "startTime": 80.3716875705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 84.6063732624,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1206.8588256000085,
          "startTime": 85.813232088
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.7090221881
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.7090221881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "デザインの調子はどうだ？",
      "startTime": 86.95559659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.05559659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい……\n全然アイデアが思いつかなくて……",
      "startTime": 90.3174635569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、最近はユニットの練習でも違和感があって\nなんだかもやもやしちゃって……",
      "startTime": 98.2796258516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.1222632567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "練習中に沙季と何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 101.1222632567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 104.2222632567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "何かがあった訳じゃないんです。ただなんとなく\nお姉ちゃんの様子がおかしい気がして……",
      "startTime": 108.7953134309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.9222632567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、前に練習を覗いた時\n沙季のダンスがいつもより大人しい気がしたが……",
      "startTime": 114.8025685219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとすると沙季は千紗を目立たせるために\nあえて自分を抑え込んでいるのかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 122.555284094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.9889299233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……そんなのダメです！\nお姉ちゃんが私のために遠慮するなんて絶対ダメです！",
      "startTime": 129.2355867079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.5889299233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "私はステージでキラキラ輝いてるお姉ちゃんを\nみんなに見てほしいんです！",
      "startTime": 137.0497371766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.1222632567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "沙季も同じように思ってるのかもしれないぞ\n頑張っている自慢の妹をみんなに見てほしくて……",
      "startTime": 142.4929045658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.95559659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことをされても私は嬉しくありません\n私のためにお姉ちゃんが自分を抑え込むなんて……",
      "startTime": 149.8772735363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.9187486489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな。そんなことをしても誰も喜ばない\nだが千紗も同じことをしようとしたじゃないか",
      "startTime": 159.4335491061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 162.8854153156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうか……私、お姉ちゃんのためって言いながら\n自分を抑え込もうとしていたんだ……",
      "startTime": 169.3976054415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.6854153156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことをしても誰も喜ばないのに……\nだから私の考えた衣装はダメだったんだ……",
      "startTime": 176.7895954071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は沙季とユニットを組むって決まった時\nどう思った？",
      "startTime": 183.6530063862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 185.0520819823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "凄く嬉しかったです……お姉ちゃんとステージに\n立てるのが嬉しくて、一緒に歌うのが楽しみで……",
      "startTime": 188.829432182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ……\n私はお姉ちゃんと一緒に歌いたかったんだ……",
      "startTime": 195.136334151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 199.5854153156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "俺も同じ気持ちだ。どちらか片方だけじゃない\n千紗と沙季が一緒に歌う姿を見たいんだ",
      "startTime": 203.7845135294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
